{{vgname|en=Half-Life 2: Deathmatch|tw=戰慄時空2：死鬥模式|cn=半衰期2：死亡竞赛|hk=tw|aka-cn=半条命2：死亡竞赛}}是由[[維爾福公司|維爾福公司]]開發的、只有[[多人电子游戏|多人模式]]的[[第一人称射击游戏|第一人称射击游戏]]。遊戲於2004年11月30日在[[Steam|Steam]]平臺發佈。《戰慄時空2：死鬥模式》使用了《[[戰慄時空2|戰慄時空2]]》的素材和遊戲引擎，加入了新地圖和新武器，並針對多人競技進行了優化。它與《[[戰慄時空|戰慄時空]]》的多人模式類似，不過它是一款獨立產品，也不包含[[戰慄時空系列|戰慄時空系列]]的遊戲劇情。此外，維爾福還公布了遊戲的部分原始碼。在許多早期的基於起源引擎的[[遊戲模組|遊戲模組]]中，多人游戏部分就是以這些原始碼為基礎製作的。

== 遊戲系統 ==

=== 個人死亡競賽 ===
[[File:Half_Life_2-_Deathmatch_Gravity_Gun.png|thumb]]
在遊戲中，玩家可以從特定的地點收集武器。一旦死亡，玩家會立刻在另外一个地點重生，生命值也會恢復到100點，但是之前得到的武器彈藥會消失。[[死亡競賽|死亡競賽]]的目標非常簡單，只要殺掉其他人就能加分。不過，自殺或死於意外會扣分。所有競賽都在各自的伺服器上面執行，每个伺服器可能有不同的規則，例如有的伺服器會限制比賽時間或最高得分。

=== 團隊死亡競賽 ===
在團隊死亡競賽中，玩家會被分為两組，一組是[[联合军|联合军]]，另一組是反抗軍。這兩組玩家的外表與《[[戰慄時空2|戰慄時空2]]》中合成人與與反抗軍的外表相同。團隊死亡競賽的規則与個人競賽相似，但團隊模式的輸贏與整個團隊的成績有關。若伺服器開啟了「隊友火力」選項，那麼射殺隊友會扣分。

== 開發 ==
在《戰慄時空2》發布之後，有評論家對遊戲沒有多人模式感到失望<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/12/01/half-life-2-deathmatch-official|title = Half-Life 2 Deathmatch Official?|date = 2004-11-30|accessdate = 2014-03-24|website = [[IGN|IGN]]|first = David|last = Adams|archivedate =2014-03-24 |deadurl = no|archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140324051035/http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/12/01/half-life-2-deathmatch-official }}</ref>。然而僅僅過了兩週，維爾福就在[[Steam|Steam]]上面正式发布了《戰慄時空2：死鬥模式》<ref name="steamann">{{Cite web|url = http://store.steampowered.com/news/364|title = Half-Life 2: Deathmatch and SDK Update|date = 2004-11-30|accessdate = 2014-03-24|website = [[Steam|Steam]]|publisher = [[威尔乌|Valve Corporation]]|archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20120928231810/http://store.steampowered.com/news/364 |deadurl = no|archivedate =2012-09-28 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.gamespot.com/articles/valve-unleashes-half-life-2-deathmatch/1100-6114195/|title = Valve unleashes Half-Life 2: Deathmatch|date = 2004-11-30|accessdate = 2014-03-24|website = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|last = Thorsen|first = Tor|archivedate =2014-03-24 |deadurl = no|archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140324051142/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/valve-unleashes-half-life-2-deathmatch/1100-6114195/ }}</ref>。維爾福在發布[[Source_SDK|Source SDK]]的同時發布遊戲，意在吸引開發者使用自家遊戲引擎製作[[遊戲模組|遊戲模組]]<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/12/01/half-life-2-deathmatch-released|title = Half-Life 2 Deathmatch Released|date = 2004-12-01|accessdate = 2014-03-23|website = [[IGN|IGN]]|last = Adams|first = David|archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20121108095226/http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/12/01/half-life-2-deathmatch-released |deadurl = no|archivedate =2012-11-08 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/news011204hl2dm|title = Valve surprises all with Half-Life 2 Deathmatch|date = 2004-12-01|accessdate = 2014-03-24|website = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|last = Bramwell|first = Tom|archivedate =2014-03-24 |deadurl = no|archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140324051257/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/news011204hl2dm }}</ref>。

在遊戲正式發布之後，維爾福仍然保持支援，例如推送新地圖、更新遊戲引擎等<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2005/02/12/another-hl2dm-map-in-the-pipe|title = Another HL2DM Map in the Pipe|date = 2005-02-11|accessdate = 2014-03-24|website = [[IGN|IGN]]|first = Tom|last = McNamara|deadurl = no|archivedate =2014-03-24 |archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140324051404/http://www.ign.com/articles/2005/02/12/another-hl2dm-map-in-the-pipe }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.gamespot.com/articles/valve-releases-details-on-future-steam-downloads/1100-6118138/|title = Valve releases details on future Steam downloads|date = 2005-02-07|accessdate = 2014-03-24|website = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|last = Surette|first = Tim|deadurl = no|archivedate =2014-03-24 |archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140324051408/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/valve-releases-details-on-future-steam-downloads/1100-6118138/ }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/news180205hl2dm|title = Valve updates HL2 Deathmatch with new weapons, map|date = 2005-02-18|accessdate = 2014-03-24|website = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|first = Tom|last = Bramwell|archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140324051430/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/news180205hl2dm |archivedate =2014-03-24 |deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[橘盒|橘盒]]不包含《戰慄時空2：死鬥模式》，但是在2010年9月維爾福把游戏引擎升級到了橙盒游戏所采用的版本。2008年1月10日，維爾福宣布擁有[[NVIDIA|NVIDIA]]顯示卡的使用者可以免費下載《戰慄時空2：死鬥模式》、《[[傳送門|传送门：仍然活着]]》、《[[戰慄時空2：消失的海岸線|戰慄時空2：消失的海岸線]]》和《{{tsl|en|Peggle Extreme}}》四款遊戲<ref name="Eurogamer">{{Cite web| first=Robert | last=Purchese | title= Portal: First Slice for NVIDIA users | date= 2008-01-10 | url =http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/portal-first-slice-for-nvidia-users | accessdate = 2014-03-24 |archivedate =2012-10-17 |deadurl = no|archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20121017014359/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/portal-first-slice-for-nvidia-users |website = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]}}</ref>

