== 評價 ==
《戰慄時空2：死鬥模式》在發布之後受到了一致好評。評論者讚揚了遊戲中的{{le|重力槍|Gravity gun}}<ref name="ignreview">{{Cite web|url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/12/02/half-life-2-deathmatch|title = Half-Life 2: Deathmatch Review|date = 2004-12-01|accessdate = 2014-03-16|last = Adams|first = Dan|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140316193051/http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/12/02/half-life-2-deathmatch|deadurl = no|archivedate = 2014-03-16|website = [[IGN|IGN]]}}</ref><ref name="gamespotreview">{{Cite web|url = http://www.gamespot.com/articles/half-life-2-deathmatch-first-impressions/1100-6114199/|title = Half-Life 2 Deathmatch First Impressions|accessdate = 2014-03-16|date = 2004-11-30|last = Kasavin|first = Greg|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140316193542/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/half-life-2-deathmatch-first-impressions/1100-6114199/|deadurl = no|archivedate = 2014-03-16|website = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]]}}</ref>。[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]稱讚次世代引擎「利用物理學的方式令人印象深刻」，並且表揚了遊戲地圖的多樣性<ref name="gamespotreview" />。[[IGN|IGN]]也對遊戲持類似的正面評價，而且高度讚揚了《戰慄時空2：死鬥模式》所產生的快節奏感<ref name="ignreview" />。

在遊戲剛發布的時候，多個評論家指出卡頓可能會對遊戲產生負面影響。但是GameSpy認為隨着伺服器數量增加，問題會逐漸得到緩解<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://pc.gamespy.com/pc/half-life-2/569798p1.html|title = Half-Life 2: Deathmatch|date = 2004-12-01|accessdate = 2014-03-24|website = [[GameSpy|GameSpy]]|last = Accardo|first = Sal|archivedate =2012-12-01 |deadurl = no|archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20121201140642/http://pc.gamespy.com/pc/half-life-2/569798p1.html }}</ref>。

